\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></li>\r\n      <li><img src=\"/assets/img/common/img_footer_logo-elbosi.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <p>&copy; 2024 SG SYSTEMS Co.,Ltd.</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</footer>\r\n\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","finalUrl":"https://www.sg-systems.co.jp/recruit/people/16/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T21:02:45.839Z"}